measurements.description: Three flowers and one bud on two 52-cm inflorescences; dorsal sepal chartreuse overlaid tesselate dark rose; synsepal pale green; petals arched, pendulous, lighter rose basally to dark rose apically, dark rose central vein; pouch light cream, exterior dark rose, dark rose and olive spots interior, fine upraised burgundy spots at rim; substance medium; texture matte.
